=== What this commit added ===
  POST /api/join { "slot": 0|1 }
  Authorization: Bearer <browser JWT>

  Relay-proxied slot claim. The browser JWT has PERMISSIONS NONE on the
  slot table (collector-only writes), so this endpoint takes the JWT,
  validates it via RETURN $auth, looks up the username with admin creds,
  and UPDATE slot:p1|p2 with admin creds. Mirror of /api/leave.

  Hardened: per-statement SQL ERR check (sql_query_as_admin only checks
  HTTP status, but constraint violations come back as per-stmt ERR).

